{"timestamp": "2025-12-03 10:14:29.714422", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission complete.\n\nSummary of what was submitted:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"leaf_router_0_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"southbound_port_mismatch\"]\n\nRecommended next actions (optional, not part of submission):\n- Move the 10.0.1.1/24 address from eth8 to eth2 on leaf_router_0_1 (or correct the physical port mapping/cabling so the host-facing link matches the interface assigned to 10.0.1.1).\n- After correction, verify by checking interface counters on both pc_0_1 and leaf_router_0_1, ARP entries, and successful pings to other hosts.\n- If you want, I can run follow-up checks (ethtool on leaf eth2/eth8, arp/bridge status, show interface counters) to confirm before/after remediation.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2349, "output_tokens": 185, "total_tokens": 2534, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 0}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
